OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779203470
OL,3,CSoldier, 24, who died at Royal Windsor
OL,4,CHorse Show was 'exceptional jockey'
OL,6,FA soldier who died after falling from
OL,7,Fher horse at the Royal Windsor Horse
OL,8,FShow has been named.
OL,10,FLance Bombardier Ciara Sullivan died
OL,11,Fon Friday and has been described by
OL,12,Fthe Ministry of Defence as an
OL,13,F"immensely professional soldier and an
OL,14,Fexceptional jockey" who was "a bright
OL,15,Flight in any room she entered".
OL,17,FDespite being given immediate medical
OL,18,Ftreatment she sustained serious
OL,19,Finjuries and died at the scene, Thames
OL,20,FValley Police said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
