OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779203470
OL,3,CSoldier, 24, who died at Royal Windsor
OL,4,CHorse Show was 'exceptional jockey'
OL,6,FThe 24-year-old joined the Army in
OL,7,FNovember 2020, attending the Army
OL,8,FTraining Centre in Pirbright, before
OL,9,Fjoining The King's Troop Royal Horse
OL,10,FArtillery in June 2021.
OL,12,FLance Bombardier Sullivan also took
OL,13,Fpart in the state funeral of the Queen
OL,14,Fin 2022, and the Coronation of King
OL,15,FCharles in 2023.
OL,17,FShe had recently qualified as an
OL,18,FAdvanced Regimental Riding Instructor
OL,19,Fand particularly enjoyed training the
OL,20,FMilitary Working Horses and developing
OL,21,Fyoung horses.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779203470
OL,3,CSoldier, 24, who died at Royal Windsor
OL,4,CHorse Show was 'exceptional jockey'
OL,6,FHer commanding officer said Ciara, who
OL,7,Fwas known as 'Sully' to her friends,
OL,8,Floved horses and had a "natural
OL,9,Faffinity" for them.
OL,11,FShe has also been described as a
OL,12,F"bright light in any room she entered".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779203470
OL,3,CSoldier, 24, who died at Royal Windsor
OL,4,CHorse Show was 'exceptional jockey'
OL,6,FA statement released by the Ministry
OL,7,Fof Defence paid tribute to Ciara: "An
OL,8,Foutstanding soldier and a role model
OL,9,Fto many she worked with. She was
OL,10,Ffearless and gifted horsewoman, having
OL,11,Fridden since childhood and having
OL,12,Fcompeted in the show-jumping ring
OL,13,Fbefore joining the Regiment; it was
OL,14,Fthis natural courage that made her
OL,15,Falways the first to volunteer to the
OL,16,Fride the most demanding of horses.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779203470
OL,3,CSoldier, 24, who died at Royal Windsor
OL,4,CHorse Show was 'exceptional jockey'
OL,6,F"Beyond her equestrian talent, she was
OL,7,Fa soldier of remarkable breadth. A
OL,8,Fskilled footballer, a dedicated
OL,9,Fpresence in the gym who pushed herself
OL,10,Fand quietly brought others along with
OL,11,Fher, and someone who found cause to
OL,12,Fcelebrate the smallest daily victories
OL,13,Fin those she served with.
OL,15,F"A natural leader and instructor, she
OL,16,Fwon the respect of all who had the
OL,17,Fprivilege of working with her, and her
OL,18,Fpatient coaching has helped many
OL,19,FMounted Gunners within the Unit fulfil
OL,20,Ftheir potential.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779203470
OL,3,CSoldier, 24, who died at Royal Windsor
OL,4,CHorse Show was 'exceptional jockey'
OL,6,F"The King's Troop Royal Horse
OL,7,FArtillery has lost not only an
OL,8,Faccomplished soldier and horsewoman,
OL,9,Fbut the kind of person who made the
OL,10,FRegiment, and the world, a better
OL,11,Fplace simply by being part of it.
OL,13,F"The thoughts of every member of The
OL,14,FTroop and The Gunners are with her
OL,15,Ffamily at this tragic time."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779203470
OL,3,CSoldier, 24, who died at Royal Windsor
OL,4,CHorse Show was 'exceptional jockey'
OL,6,FLt Gen MR Elviss CB, MBE, COMARRC and
OL,7,FMaster Gunner St James Palace said:
OL,8,F"The shock of LBdr Ciara Sullivan's
OL,9,Floss is profound. A fine soldier, she
OL,10,Fdied doing a job she loved surrounded
OL,11,Fby people who held her in the highest
OL,12,Fregard. A dedicated, committed and
OL,13,Fhighly respected junior commander; she
OL,14,Fwill be sorely missed.
OL,16,F"The Royal Regiment of Artillery and
OL,17,Fthe wider British Army is a lesser
OL,18,Fplace without her. I could not be more
OL,19,Fsorry nor saddened by her loss and my
OL,20,Fthoughts, prayers and condolences are
OL,21,Fwith her family and friends."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779203470
OL,3,CSoldier, 24, who died at Royal Windsor
OL,4,CHorse Show was 'exceptional jockey'
OL,6,FDefence Secretary John Healey MP said:
OL,7,F"Lance Bombardier Ciara Sullivan was a
OL,8,Fbrilliant young soldier who served our
OL,9,Fnation with dedication. We're all
OL,10,Fdeeply shocked and saddened by her
OL,11,Fdeath.
OL,13,F"My thoughts are with Ciara's family,
OL,14,Floved ones and colleagues at this
OL,15,Fdevastating time."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
